{"tid":2449032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揭印中邊境共軍被活埋   中国富商子被公安海外追捕","createTime":"2021-03-16T10:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T13:21:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5f6ebbfde4c91f1b6b6b0b97d1e148c55f3d5070","tid":2449032,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:52:33.000Z","msg":"北京警方3月15號發布通報，對大陸知名地產商潘石屹的兒子潘瑞展開「跨境追逃」。原因是，潘瑞去年在微博上曝光中共軍方在中印邊境衝突中至少有「一個營地被活埋」。<br />\n<br />\n北京海淀公安分局官方微博15號通報表示，潘某曾於2020年6月23號，在他人微博評論區, 發表質疑中印邊境共軍傷亡人數的言論，潘某已於同年2月2號出國，此後一直待在境外；目前「已依法對潘某刑事拘留，並對其開展追逃」。<br />\n<br />\n中共多家媒體報導，被北京警方｢跨境追逃」的微博用戶「潘某」，疑似地產商潘石屹之子潘瑞。<br />\n<br />\n根據微博截圖，潘瑞確實於2020年6月23號在微博跟帖中留言說：「至少一個營地被活埋&hellip;&hellip;沒有機會被天葬了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/03/16/a103074716.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2Fa103074716.html&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=b1a5d5ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/03/16/a103074716.html</a>"},{"pid":"74e0ab220a3719c1509fbd4d529feb18300e3d35","tid":2449032,"uid":151074,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:48:02.000Z","msg":"新唐人唔好傳聞當新聞，自己filter 下會好好多"},{"pid":"a14aa8ab5a696be9545a7cd43f54ad5cf6dcbf76","tid":2449032,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"74e0ab220a3719c1509fbd4d529feb18300e3d35","tid":2449032,"uid":151074,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:48:02.000Z","msg":"新唐人唔好傳聞當新聞，自己filter 下會好好多"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:29:44.000Z","msg":"咁你filter完未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4b3a79e721d5887fafc576556035c4f32c8bb5","tid":2449032,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a14aa8ab5a696be9545a7cd43f54ad5cf6dcbf76","tid":2449032,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"74e0ab220a3719c1509fbd4d529feb18300e3d35","tid":2449032,"uid":1510