個營地被印度活埋了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（微博網頁截圖）<br />\n去年6月中旬，中印邊境駐軍爆發嚴重流血衝突後，印度軍方宣布，印方有20名軍人在衝突中死亡，數十人受傷，而中共軍方卻一直不肯對外公布己方的傷亡人數。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">一時間，有關中共軍人傷亡的各種傳言四起，而潘瑞在微博上所提到的「活埋」說法，只是其中的一種。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/mkt_ipad/2021/03/15/a103074191.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2Fmkt_ipad%2F2021%2F03%2F15%2Fa103074191.html&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=fec09c91\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/mkt_ipad/2021/03/15/a103074191.html</a>"},{"pid":"be424e7aa5212b6839133403c7301c415b5ac160","tid":2449032,"uid":66378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"潘某已於同年2月2號出國，此後一直待在境外；目前「已依法對潘某刑事拘留，並對其開展追逃」。<br />\n<br />\n呢句野1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n追逃？想講追捕？<br />\n點樣又扣留但又追捕？"},{"pid":"ecc5ae90af1bce74315fedf16acc2d4c255bfbb0","tid":2449032,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e0ab220a3719c1509fbd4d529feb18300e3d35","tid":2449032,"uid":151074,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:48:02.000Z","msg":"新唐人唔好傳聞當新聞，自己filter 下會好好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"rthk 中國點點點今次都有講"},{"pid":"a3f9f83d5576499503c1c6e3a0354a546a9e46d6","tid":2449032,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1e3b468a78424018a2e7ad6489f5c24a35efdf7","tid":2449032,"uid":278219,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e0ab220a3719c1509fbd4d529feb18300e3d35","tid":2449032,"uid":151074,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:48:02.000Z","msg":"新唐人唔好傳聞當新聞，自己filter 下會好好多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"on9 大把新聞都有報呀<br />\nfil撚左你就差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T13:11:53.000Z","msg":"大把即係邊度？汁呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c